  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "It seems `react-instantsearch` doesn't work well with webpack 2 tree shaking.\r\n```js\r\nimport a from './a'\r\nimport b from './b'\r\nimport c from './c'\r\nimport { SearchBox } from 'react-instantsearch/dom'\r\n\r\nexport default listing = () => {\r\n  a()\r\n  b()\r\n  c()\r\n  console.log(typeof SearchBox)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n![webpack](http://i.imgur.com/wnQwR7L.png)\r\n\r\nThe overall size is quite big, 114KB gzipped. For a progressive web app, it's really big deal.\r\n ",
