    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Another idea that might work is adding a new build target that transpiles to es5, except the import/export. Then that folder should be added as `module` in the package.json\r\n\r\nOlder rollup supported `jsnext:main`, but also switched to `module`. \r\n\r\nsources:\r\n\r\n* https://github.com/webpack/webpack/issues/1979\r\n* https://github.com/dherman/defense-of-dot-js/blob/master/proposal.md\r\n* https://github.com/rollup/rollup/wiki/pkg.module",
